                "name": "Chilling Touch",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A yuki-onna\u2019s touch causes 4d6 cold damage. Whenever a creature takes cold damage in this manner, it must make a DC 20 Fortitude save to avoid being staggered by the supernatural cold for 1 round. This duration stacks. The save DC is Charisma-based."
