                "name": "Snow Dependency",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A yuki-onna is staggered if she is ever in an area without snow while her snowstorm aura is suppressed or otherwise not functioning."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Snowstorm",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A yuki-onna is surrounded by whirling blasts of snow, even in areas that wouldn\u2019t allow for such weather, that comprise a 200-foot-radius spread. Within this area, the snowfall and wind gusts cause a \u20134 penalty on Perception checks and ranged attacks. The wind itself blows in a clockwise rotation around the yuki-onna, and functions as severe wind (<i>Core Rulebook </i>439). A yuki-onna is unaffected by snowstorms or blizzards of any kind. Any effect that causes these winds to drop below severe (such as <i>control weather </i>or <i>control winds</i>) cancels the snowstorm effect entirely."
            }
